For Thursday, March 24 you are to watch the following two tutorials on using Adobe Animate CC.
1. Introduction: https://youtu.be/iEZe8GwV4sk
2. Adding vector graphics to the stage: https://youtu.be/RuvXf9RLnKE


For Thursday, you also should create an Animate document and place the following on it:
1. All bar chart bars (each nation should have its own layer) Get the bars here: /weekly_readings_and_assignments/Olympic_Bars.ai
2. A layer with all text labels
3. A layer with the gray separators behind the chart

You do NOT need to:
1. Create the toggles that turn the bars on and off
2. Create the pop ups with contextual date information
